Metadata: Social indicators for the Washington Coast Integrated Ecosystem Assessment
Report to Washington Department of Natural Resources in fulfillment of Interagency Agreement No. IAA 14-204

This report documents the development and assessment of social indicators of human wellbeing for the four counties of Washington State's Pacific Coast: Clallam, Jefferson, Grays Harbor, and Pacific counties. The social indicators assessment is part of the Washington integrated ecosystem assessment to support the science needs for Washington marine spatial planning.
